Test Case Group: Product Search

Basic Search
1.1. Search with a valid product name.
1.2. Search with a partial product name.
1.3. Attempt a search with a product name that doesn't exist in the database.
1.4. Attempt a search using spaces only.


Typographical Tolerance
3.1. Search for "buter" and expect "butter" results.
3.2. Intentionally misspell a product name to check for suggestions or close matches.
3.3. Search with mixed case input like "BuTteR" and expect relevant results.
